{"title":"hexo博客杂谈","slug":"hexo博客杂谈","date":"2021-07-20T06:52:03.000Z","updated":"2021-07-22T08:05:59.299Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hexo博客杂谈.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"写一些用hexo写博客时常用的东西  ","covers":["https://upload-bbs.mihoyo.com/upload/2021/07/20/184593067/2a03b66fdf1551d53ddbdf8e2fbbba90_3182517286345932096.jpg?x-oss-process=image//resize,s_500/quality,q_80/auto-orient,0/interlace,1/format,jpg","https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B2%7D"],"content":"<p>写一些用hexo写博客时常用的东西  </p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<p>神里镇文<br><img src=\"https://upload-bbs.mihoyo.com/upload/2021/07/20/184593067/2a03b66fdf1551d53ddbdf8e2fbbba90_3182517286345932096.jpg?x-oss-process=image//resize,s_500/quality,q_80/auto-orient,0/interlace,1/format,jpg\" alt=\"神里我老婆！！！\"><br>对图片“查看源代码”有彩蛋</p>\n<h2 id=\"为文章添加多个标签\"><a href=\"#为文章添加多个标签\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"为文章添加多个标签\"></a>为文章添加多个标签</h2><p>在你的markdown文件头部，也就是俩<code>---</code>之间的部分，添加如下代码：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight subunit\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">tags:</span> [标签1, 标签2, 标签3]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>当然，这样也是可以的：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight subunit\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">tags:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">-_标签1_</span><br><span class=\"line\">-_标签2_</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>上面写的<code>_</code>是空格的意思，<code>-</code>和标签后面都必须有一个空格。</p>\n<h2 id=\"截取文章摘要\"><a href=\"#截取文章摘要\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"截取文章摘要\"></a>截取文章摘要</h2><p>手动在文章合适的位置添加<code>&lt;!--more--&gt;</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"给文章置顶\"><a href=\"#给文章置顶\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"给文章置顶\"></a>给文章置顶</h2><p>简单粗暴的方法：把date改成99999-12-31 23:59:59<br>然后就是使用现成的库  </p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ npm uninstall hexo-generator-index --save</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ npm install hexo-generator-index-pin-top --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>然后在你的文章前面的<code>---</code>之间加上<code>top: true</code>即可，比如说：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">---</span><br><span class=\"line\">title: 友情链接</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\">top: true</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>如果想直接修改主题的文件，你也可以参考<a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/42a4efcdf8d7\">这篇文章</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"草稿\"><a href=\"#草稿\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"草稿\"></a>草稿</h2><p>我不用草稿……</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo new draft 文章名称</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo n draft 文章名称</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"使用LaTeX\"><a href=\"#使用LaTeX\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用LaTeX\"></a>使用LaTeX</h2><p><strong>首先要保证你的主题是支持LaTeX的！！！</strong>我配置了两个小时都没成功，最后发现是Lite主题不支持LaTeX……<br>但是我的主题不支持，所以我只好用知乎的开放API……也就是<code>https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=</code>，效果：  <img src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B2%7D\" alt=\"图片挂了QAQ……\">当然url里的任何\\都要换成%5C</p>\n","categories":[{"name":"hexo","slug":"hexo","count":2,"path":"api/categories/hexo.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"长期更新","slug":"长期更新","count":2,"path":"api/tags/长期更新.json"},{"name":"hexo","slug":"hexo","count":2,"path":"api/tags/hexo.json"},{"name":"杂谈","slug":"杂谈","count":1,"path":"api/tags/杂谈.json"}]}